Valley Of Death version 1.3 is available for download on Google Drive.
To start playing Valley Of Death, simply follow the steps down below.

1. Go to this link: https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B_vswrjBhyxUQzlSVy1vY1lJRHc
2. At the top right of the screen there should be a button which will let you
   download the zip file. Click this button and download the zip file.
3. On your computer, bring the zip file to a good location, for example, the Desktop.
4. Unzip the zip file so that you now have a regular folder.
5. To play the game, double click the folder, then double click the .exe program.
